'''Camp O'pera''' is a former settlement and mining camp in [[Amador County, California|Amador County]], [[California]]. It was founded in the summer of 1849 near [[French Camp, Amador County, California|French Camp]].<ref name=CGN>{{California's Geographic Names|511}}</ref> 

